            "title": "維昇招股價68.8元近下限  認購20手穩獲1 手",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">維昇藥業 (02561)公布招股價68.8元，較招股價下限68.44元高約0.53%，香港公開發售部分超額認購約71.64倍。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"維昇藥業招股書封面\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/02561.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"維昇藥業招股書封面\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/02561.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">維昇藥業招股書封面</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">招股價介乎68.44元至75.28元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">認購一手100股份配比率6.27%，須認購20手即2000股方穩獲一手。維昇藥業於今日上午9時掛牌買賣。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">集團指，香港公開發售部分觸發回補機制，發售股份數目升至455.4萬股，佔發售股份總數比重升至40%，而「頂頭槌飛」共有25人申請，涉申請49.5萬股，各獲分配3.28萬股，以及其中8人獲額外100股。至於國際發售部分超額認購約0.65倍。該集團招股集資約7.83億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">維昇藥業此次IPO引入了5名基石投資者，包括安科生物、蘇州工業園區產業投資基金、Vivo Capital、藥明生物、Reynold Lemkins等。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">三家暗盤交易場中，維昇暗盤跌幅5.7%至7.2%，收報63.85元至64.9元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14792567-%e7%b6%ad%e6%98%87%e6%8b%9b%e8%82%a1%e5%83%b968-8%e5%85%83%e8%bf%91%e4%b8%8b%e9%99%90-%e8%aa%8d%e8%b3%bc20%e6%89%8b%e7%a9%a9%e7%8d%b21-%e6%89%8b",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/20250210_FI_source-web_Visen-2.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-03-21 08:35:41",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "黑期跌185點  ADR低水188點  阿里低近2%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">新加坡黑期跌185點或0.76%，報24043。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股ADR較恆指昨日收市低收188點或0.78%，報24031點。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"阿里巴巴官網圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/bplib_20230829-130621_20230810_FI_source-web_阿里巴巴-3_source-web__704px.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"阿里巴巴官網圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/bplib_20230829-130621_20230810_FI_source-web_阿里巴巴-3_source-web__704px.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">阿里巴巴官網圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">主要股份ADR普遍低水， 阿里巴巴(09988) ADR較港收市價較港收市價低1.8%，折合133.01港元 ;  攜程(09961) ADR較香港收市價低1%，折合501.54元 ; 騰訊(00700)ADR收市折合港幣514.05元，較香港收市價低1% ; 小米(01810) ADR較香港收市價低0.3%，折合56.35港元 ; 美團(03690) ADR較香港收市價低0.5%，折合167.18元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滙控(00005)ADR折合港元計收報89.55元，較香港收市價低0.3% ; 友邦保險(01299) ADR收市折合港幣61.74元，較香港收市價低0.8% ;  港交所(00388) ADR收市折合港幣367.62元，較香港收市價低0.5%;  中國平安(02318) ADR收市折合港幣48.61元，較香港收市價低1.4% 。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒指夜市期指收報24065點，跌128點，較昨日恒指收市24219點，低水155點，成交21128張。國指夜市期指收報8895點，較昨日國指收市低水55點。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14792550-%e9%bb%91%e6%9c%9f%e8%b7%8c185%e9%bb%9e-adr%e4%bd%8e%e6%b0%b4188%e9%bb%9e-%e9%98%bf%e9%87%8c%e4%bd%8e%e8%bf%912",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/09/HK-STOCK_ADR-1_source-bp_-2.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-03-21 08:25:53",
